item.title: Webclient Help
item.dc:creator: @Aceron4 Aceron4
item.description:
@Aceron4 wrote:

You either put “client.jar” there (or whatever you called your .jar file)

OR

You put in the link to the client.jar file of wherever you uploaded it. (ie. If you uploaded to dropbox copy and paste the public download link into there)

If you need more help let me know.
